CustomField.formula: IF(ISBLANK(Birthdate), "No Birthdate", IF((TODAY() - Birthdate) / 365 < 10, "Under 10", IF((TODAY() - Birthdate) / 365 < 20, "10-19", IF((TODAY() - Birthdate) / 365 < 30, "20-29", IF((TODAY() - Birthdate) / 365 < 40, "30-39", IF((TODAY() - Birthdate) / 365 < 50, "40-49", IF((TODAY() - Birthdate) / 365 < 60, "50-59", IF((TODAY() - Birthdate) / 365 < 70, "60-69", IF((TODAY() - Birthdate) / 365 >= 70, "70+", "N/A")))))))))
CustomField.label: Age Group
